<item>
            <title>[FLINK-33248] Calling CURRENT_WATERMARK without parameters gives IndexOutOfBoundsException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-33248</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Create a table&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
Flink SQL&amp;gt; CREATE TABLE T (ts TIMESTAMP(3)) WITH (&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;connector&apos;&lt;/span&gt;=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;values&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;bounded&apos;&lt;/span&gt;=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;);
[INFO] Execute statement succeed. &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Select CURRENT_WATERMARK without parameters&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
Flink SQL&amp;gt; SELECT ts, CURRENT_WATERMARK() FROM T;
[ERROR] Could not execute SQL statement. Reason:
java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException: Index 0 out of bounds &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; length 0 &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Logs from sql-client:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
2023-10-11 14:58:20,576 ERROR org.apache.flink.table.gateway.service.operation.OperationManager [] - Failed to execute the operation cc8d29d3-e6ad-428a-92ea-b0a2a72c25f9.
org.apache.flink.table.api.ValidationException: SQL validation failed. Unexpected error in type inference logic of function &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;CURRENT_WATERMARK&apos;&lt;/span&gt;. This is a bug.
&#160; &#160; at org.apache.flink.table.planner.calcite.FlinkPlannerImpl.org$apache$flink$table$planner$calcite$FlinkPlannerImpl$$validate(FlinkPlannerImpl.scala:200) ~[?:?]
